commitment removal. After all changes in a Bill scenario is made satisfactorily, you can
call this API with a Bill scenario ID to generate the Bill estimate. Bill estimate
calculates the pre-tax cost for your consolidated billing family, incorporating all modeled
usage and commitments alongside existing usage and commitments from your most recent
completed anniversary bill, with any applicable discounts applied.

